The recommended installation procedure:
1) configure: cmake -S . -B build -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/path/to/install/tree [+ other CMake vars, such as CMAKE_CXX_COMPILER]
2) (optional) test: cmake --build build --target check
3) install: cmake --build build --target install:

Report all problems to https://github.com/evaleev/libint/issues

